data.description: Check out this great floorplan in an awesome location!  This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is open concept, with a beautifully updated interior! Updates completed in 2021 include freshly painted cabinets and new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the home- no carpet!! The home also has a new roof (installed in July of 2022), and a new HVAC system (installed in June 2023).  A separate dining area, split master bedroom, dedicated laundry room, and covered patio are just a few more of the many reasons the designed layout, features and flow of this home cannot be beat. Near schools & major shopping with easy access to 1604 & IH 35N.
